<div id="pf6" class="pf w1 h1" data-page-no="6"><div class="pc pc6 w1 h1"><div class="c x10 y78 w2 h14"><div class="t m3 x11 h15 y79 ff11 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Mission to the Chinese </div><div class="t m4 x12 h16 y7a ff11 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Mandarin Chinese is the most widely spoken language in the world. </div><div class="t m4 x12 h16 y7b ff11 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Well over a billion people speak Mandarin, Cantonese, or one of several </div><div class="t m4 x13 h16 y7c ff11 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">other languages and dialects that originated in China. Millions of </div><div class="t m4 x14 h16 y7d ff11 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Chinese-speaking people live throughout Asia, North America, and dozens </div><div class="t m4 x15 h16 y7e ff11 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of other countries around the world. In North America Chinese is the </div><div class="t m4 x15 h16 y7f ff11 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">third most widely spoken language.</div><div class="t m4 x16 h16 y80 ff11 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Yet until recently, few video programs have been produced in one of the </div><div class="t m4 x16 h16 y81 ff11 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Chinese languages. The church is striving to make God’s message available </div><div class="t m4 xa h16 y82 ff11 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to Chinese-speaking populations wherever they live through avenues such </div><div class="t m4 xa h16 y83 ff11 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as the Internet and Hope Channel. I’m glad that this quarter part of my </div><div class="t m4 x17 h16 y84 ff11 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Thirteenth Sabbath Offering will help make more programming available to </div><div class="t m4 xe h16 y85 ff11 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Chinese-speaking people around the world. For me, it’s personal.</div></div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
